#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:22
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Info is a type of documentation. The documents are in a file format called "
"texinfo, and can be read on the command line with the <ulink url=\"info:/info"
"\"><command>info</command></ulink> program."
msgstr ""
"Info é un tipo de documentación. Os documentos están nun formato de ficheiro "
"chamado texinfo, e poden lerse na liña de ordes mediante o programa <ulink "
"url=\"info:/info\"><command>info</command></ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:26
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Info KIO worker allows you to read the info pages installed on your "
"system, from within &konqueror;. You can use it very easily:"
msgstr ""
"O traballador de KIO «Info» permítelle ler desde &konqueror; as páxinas de "
"información instaladas no sistema. Usalo é moi fácil:"

#. Tag: screen
#: index.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput><command>info:</command><replaceable>gcc</replaceable></userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput><command>info:</command><replaceable>gcc</replaceable></userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:31
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This would show you the top level node of the Info documentation for the "
"&gcc; compiler."
msgstr ""
"Isto amosaralle o nodo superior da documentación Info do compilador &gcc;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Info is a &GNU; replacement for <command>man</command>, but is not widely "
"used outside of &GNU; software."
msgstr ""
"Info é o substituto de &GNU; de <command>man</command>, pero non se usa "
"habitualmente fóra dos programas de &GNU;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can quite easily browse the info documentation you have installed from "
"within the &khelpcenter; application, or you can use the info KIO worker "
"directly from within both &konqueror; and the mini-cli."
msgstr ""
"Pode navegar dun xeito sinxelo pola documentación de Info que teña instalada "
"mediante a aplicación &khelpcenter;, ou pode usar o traballador de KIO info "
"directamente tanto desde &konqueror; como desde o mini-cli."
